                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8220" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0243</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3437 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内控留痕，弊过有证：小微企业南孺公司舞弊“连环”现形记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internal control left traces and fraud has been proved: Small and micro enterprises Nanru company fraud “serial” manifest</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李万福，陆汉娟，张鹏飞，王艺蒙，孟翠湖，薛天竺，姜文丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京孺子牛物业服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">维修部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制；内部控制痕迹； 反舞弊；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internal control; Internal control trace; Anti-fraud</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">囿于规模和资源，小微企业的内部控制往往较为薄弱，易滋生职业舞弊行为，那么，小微企业应该如何通过强化内部控制于事前有效防范舞弊？如何借助不同内部控制痕迹之间的关联性于事后及时识别舞弊呢？本案例以小微企业南孺公司员工“连环”舞弊事件为例，从舞弊者与破解者双视角生动再现了维修工小张利用内部控制漏洞倒卖维修物资和违规收取维修费进行“连环”舞弊的手法、管理者通过内控运行产生的各类痕迹逐步破解小张舞弊行为的过程，深度解析了小微企业南孺公司维修物资领用、维修存货盘点及维修收费等环节的内部控制缺陷，强调了如何利用内部控制痕迹识别舞弊并根据舞弊隐患完善小微企业内部控制，旨在引导学生体会内部控制的反舞弊作用，培养其借助内控痕迹防范和识别舞弊的能力，为其他小微企业的反舞弊内部控制建设提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Limited by scale and resources, the internal control of small and micro enterprises is often weak, which is easy to breed professional fraud. So, how should them effectively prevent fraud in advance by strengthening internal control? How to use the correlation between different traces of internal control to identify fraud after the fact? This case takes the “serial” fraud incident of employees in small and micro enterprises Nanru company as an example, and vividly reproduces the “serial” fraud method of maintenance worker Xiao Zhang using internal control loopholes to resend maintenance materials and illegally collect maintenance fees from the perspective of both fraudsters and decoders, and the process of managers gradually cracking Zhang’s fraud through various traces generated by internal control operation. This case deeply analyzes the internal control defects of Nanru company in such aspects as the acquisition of maintenance materials, maintenance inventory and maintenance charges, and emphasizes how to use internal control traces to identify fraud and improve the internal control of small and micro enterprises according to the hidden dangers of fraud. It aims to guide students to understand the anti-fraud role of internal control and cultivate their ability to prevent and identify fraud with the help of internal control traces. It can provide reference for the construction of anti-fraud internal control of other small and micro enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《内部控制审计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制要素；舞弊动因理论；风险管理理论；控制活动的一般方法等</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
